patthana14.33:1.1_0: Pariyāpannaṁ dhammaṁ paṭicca naapariyāpanno dhammo uppajjati hetupaccayā.
patthana14.33:2.1_0: Apariyāpannaṁ dhammaṁ paṭicca naapariyāpanno dhammo uppajjati hetupaccayā.
patthana14.33:2.1_1: Apariyāpannaṁ dhammaṁ paṭicca napariyāpanno dhammo uppajjati hetupaccayā.
patthana14.33:2.1_2: Apariyāpannaṁ dhammaṁ paṭicca napariyāpanno ca naapariyāpanno ca dhammā uppajjanti hetupaccayā.
patthana14.33:3.1_0: Pariyāpannañca apariyāpannañca dhammaṁ paṭicca naapariyāpanno dhammo uppajjati hetupaccayā.
patthana14.33:4.1_0: Hetuyā pañca, ārammaṇe dve …pe… avigate pañca.
